            Provenance Schema, Bylaws / Charter, and Dispute Resolution.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Monday May 11, 2026 — Site update v33: Documentation + Polish — procedures manual, public contributors, notification inbox, profile editor.</strong>
            v32 opened the engagement breadth; v33 closes it. A new <a href="/how-the-library-works/">/how-the-library-works/</a>
            procedures manual ships with eleven plain-prose pages (index + ten role pages — visitors, readers,
